      <para>
        As an example to get all account types that identifier matchs exacly <emphasis>111</emphasis> formulate:
      </para>
      <!--
      Don't indent what's in the element below
      -->
      <programlisting language="bash">
filter=id eq "111"
      </programlisting>
    </section>
